<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Itinerari</title>
    <!-- loading jquery -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <!-- favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" href="favicon (2).ico" />
    <!-- bootstrap -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      integrity="sha384-B0vP5xmATw1+K9KRQjQERJvTumQW0nPEzvF6L/Z6nronJ3oUOFUFpCjEUQouq2+l"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <!-- my css -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/style3.css" />

    <!-- css for styleIti -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/styleIti.css" />

    <!-- font-awesome -->
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/7091884191.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>

    <!-- bootstrap scripts -->
    <script
      src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-9/reFTGAW83EW2RDu2S0VKaIzap3H66lZH81PoYlFhbGU+6BZp6G7niu735Sk7lN"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-+YQ4JLhjyBLPDQt//I+STsc9iw4uQqACwlvpslubQzn4u2UU2UFM80nGisd026JF"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- NAVBAR -->
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="row">
        <div
          class="col-md-12 navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-dark bg-dark"
          style="padding-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 15px"
        >
          <a
            href="/"
            class="logo navbar-brand text-white offset-md-2"
            style="margin-left: 50px"
            >VIROM</a
          >
          <button
            class="navbar-toggler"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#navbarNav"
            aria-controls="navbarNav"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-label="Toggle navigation"
          >
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav ml-auto" style="margin-right: 30px">
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item active">
                <a href="/itinerari" class="nav-link">Itinerari</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a href="/aboutus" class="nav-link">About Us</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item" style="padding: 5px 0 0 20px">
                <img
                  id="modal-btn"
                  style="width: 25px"
                  src="image/User_Avatar_2.png"
                  alt=""
                />
                <div id="my-modal" class="modal">
                  <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                      <h2 style="color: white">User information</h2>
                      <span class="close">&times;</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                      <p>First Name: <%= firstName %></p>
                      <p>Last Name: <%= lastName %></p>
                      <p>Username: <%= username %></p>
                      <a
                        class="btn btn-dark btn-md"
                        style="float: right"
                        href="/logout"
                        role="button"
                        >Log Out</a
                      >
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <section class="itinerari">
      <h1
        style="
          font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
          font-weight: bold;
          color: black;
        "
      >
        ITINERARI A TEMPO
      </h1>
      <h3
        style="
          text-align: center;
          font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
          padding-bottom: 30px;
          font-size: 1.5rem;
          width: 70%;
          color: black;
          margin: 20px auto 20px auto;
        "
      >
        I nostri itinerari ti aiuterà a organizzare il viaggio e a risparmiare,
        visitando i migliori punti d’interesse della Città Eterna, in un giorno
        o più, fornendovi itinerari studiati ad hoc per godere delle bellezze di
        questa antica città. Proponiamo dei itinerari emozionanti e suggestivi
        per chi desidera conoscere le imperdibili attrazioni della città in modo
        migliore.
      </h3>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="itinerari-review">
              <div class="card">
                <a href="/itinerari/24ore">
                  <img
                    class="img-fluid"
                    style="height: 235px"
                    src="image/info_coloseo.jpg"
                /></a>
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>Itinerari in 24 Ore</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="itinerari-review">
              <div class="card">
                <a href="/itinerari/48ore">
                  <img
                    class="img-fluid"
                    style="height: 235px"
                    src="image/fontana_iti.jpg"
                /></a>
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>Itinerari in 48 Ore</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="itinerari-review">
              <div class="card">
                <a href="/itinerari/72ore"
                  ><img
                    class="img-fluid"
                    style="height: 235px"
                    src="image/info_coloseo.jpg"
                /></a>
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>Itinerari in 72 Ore</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <footer class="w-section" id="footer">
      <i class="fab fa-twitter download-class2"></i>
      <i class="fab fa-facebook-f download-class2"></i>
      <i class="fab fa-instagram download-class2"></i>
      <i class="fas fa-envelope download-class2"></i>
      <p
        style="
          size: 12;
          text-align: center;
          color: #fff;
          font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
          margin-bottom: 0px;
        "
      >
        © Copyright 2021 C&J's.Inc
      </p>
    </footer>
    <script src="js/openmodal.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
  </body>
</html>
